Satoshi
=======

Designed by the Indian Type Foundry (ITF).
Obtained from Fontshare: https://www.fontshare.com/fonts/satoshi

Licensed under the Fontshare / ITF Free Font License, which permits use in
desktop, web, and application projects (including embedding in software).
Full license terms: https://www.fontshare.com/licenses/itf-ffl

Bundled in this directory:
  - Satoshi-Medium.woff2  (weight 500)
  - Satoshi-Bold.woff2    (weight 700)

Used only on GitChef brand surfaces (wordmark, headings); the rest of the UI
uses the platform system font stack.
